{
  "stem": "17135.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because until that night, although there were boycotts, there were individual persecution of-- of-- of individuals, there were the Nuremberg Law, that deprived the Jews of making a living, throwing them out from all their professions.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were not allowed to work in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- in-- in universities.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were totally outcast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they still could make a living.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they-- they were boycotting the stores with signs to don't buy from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The Jews are our-- our-- our-- our-- our-- [GERMAN]-- our misfortune, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But in Kristallnacht, [? it ?] was a very frightening experience.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and I remember on November the 9th, first of all, we saw the-- the synagogue was inside where we lived.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We saw the synagogue burning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we heard the noise and the screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Most of those, they were not SS.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were SA.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[GERMAN], they called them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They were not as young.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were more of the elderly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "SR, they call it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "SA in English.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And some of them were literally drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they went from store to store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there were few other Jewish stores, not much further we lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In Germany at that time, it was customary that you had a store on the ground floor and you lived upstairs.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lived in the fourth floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was a nice building.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember we heard the screaming.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and-- and it broke all the-- the-- the-- the big windows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and by force, they-- they-- they broke the-- the-- the-- the iron door and-- and went-- and started destroying everything and burning everything.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We smelled the-- the fire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, the most frightening thing was, they were knocking at the door.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
